Devouring Plague transforms your next Mind Flay into Mind Flay: Insanity. Lasts {1} sec.

|T425954:24|t {ffffffff|Mind Flay: Insanity}
Assaults the target's mind with Shadow energy, causing {2} Shadow damage over {3} sec and slowing their movement speed by {4}%.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {5} Insanity over the duration.}

Assault an enemy's mind, dealing {1} Shadow damage and briefly reversing their perception of reality.

For {2} sec, the next {3} damage they deal will heal their target, and the next {4} healing they deal will damage their target.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {5} Insanity.}

Summons a Psyfiend with {1} health for {2} sec beside you to attack the target at range with Psyflay.

|T136208:24|t {ffffffff|Psyflay}
Deals up to {3}% of the target's total health in Shadow damage every {4} sec. Also slows their movement speed by {5}% and reduces healing received by {6}%.

|T2101983:24|t {ffffffff|Sanguine Teachings}
Sanguine Teachings grants an additional {1}% Leech.

|T136230:24|t {ffffffff|Vampiric Embrace}
Reduces the cooldown of Vampiric Embrace by {2} sec, increases its healing done by {3}%.
